      <back>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Only the lower portion of this tombstone remains, containing the letter N and an engraved "Tree of Life." Based on many similar Greek tombstones, the N, being the last letter on the stone, can be assumed to denote the age of the deceased person. The Tree of Life, while it was a Jewish symbol in origin, was commonly borrowed by Christians and thus its presence does not decisively indicate religion. Dimensions given are for entire stone, not just inscribed area.</p>
         </div>
